  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      What are two common causes of signal degradation when using UTP cabling? (Choose two.)
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-18">
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">loss of light over long distances</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">low-quality cable or connectors</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">low-quality shielding in cable</span>
